entry.title: Videohog for Mac has been submitted to Apple for review.
entry.content: I have submitted Videohog to Apple, it is currently in the 'Waiting for Export Compliance' stage. This is due to the app making use of HTTPS/SSL for the use of private/secure authentication and web transfers.

entry.title: Videohog for Mac coming soon...
entry.content: Videohog is in it's final stages of development for release. It will provide a way for videos to be downloaded off website's at the maximum speed of your internet connection.
